## Introduction

This project is a beginner-friendly PHP application that showcases the fundamental concepts of PHP programming. It includes examples of variables, functions, loops, and more.

## Features

- Basic PHP syntax and structure
- Examples of common PHP functions
- Simple form handling
- Database connection and queries

